**Description: This is a futuristic technology room, illuminated by multicolored LED lights. The walls are covered in glass panels displaying the outside city, while high-tech equipment takes up most of the space. In the center of the room, there is a large table with touch screens and various technological devices, such as state-of-the-art computers, tablets, smartphones, and even virtual reality goggles. A large server stands out in one corner of the room, with monitors displaying real-time graphics and data. In another corner, there is a small meeting room with comfortable chairs and equipped with a projector and projection screen. There is also a bookshelf with technical manuals and shelves housing a variety of gadgets and accessories, such as drones, cameras, headphones, and even a 3D printer. The adjacent terrace houses solar panels that power the entire room with clean, renewable energy. Style: Futuristic Colors: Variations of blue and green, with highlights in neon tones. Mandatory elements: Glass panels, server, touch screens, technological devices, meeting room, bookshelf, shelves with gadgets and accessories, terrace with solar panels.
